text: José C. Paz Partido is a partido in the Greater Buenos Aires urban area of Buenos Aires Province in Argentina. The provincial subdivision has a population of 263,094 inhabitants in an area of , and its capital city is José Clemente Paz, which is from Buenos Aires. ==Economy== The main industries in J.C. Paz Partido are centered on the production of textiles, ceramics and food. ==References== ==External links== * Jose C.
